<h2>Q1: YouTube & Cocomelon OK ba?</h2>

<p><strong>A1:</strong></p>

<p>Masyadong addictive ang Cocomelon dahil sa fast visuals at repetition.</p>

<h3>1. Problema</h3>
<ul>
<li>Passive learning</li>
<li>Nawawala ang real interaction</li>
</ul>

<h3>2. Detox Strategy</h3>
<ul>
<li>Bawasan gradually</li>
<li>Use visual timer</li>
</ul>

<h3>3. Convert to real play</h3>
<ul>
<li>Use toys</li>
<li>Sing with child</li>
</ul>

<h3>4. Rule of 3</h3>
<ul>
<li>Watch 15m</li>
<li>Play 15m</li>
<li>Move 15m</li>
</ul>

</div>

<div lang="jp">
<h2>Q1: YouTubeは使っていい？</h2>

<p><strong>A1:</strong></p>

<p>刺激が強く依存しやすいです。</p>

<h3>1. 問題</h3>
<ul>
<li>受動的学習</li>
<li>対人関係が減る</li>
</ul>

<h3>2. 対策</h3>
<ul>
<li>徐々に減らす</li>
<li>タイマー使用</li>
</ul>

<h3>3. 現実遊びへ</h3>
<ul>
<li>おもちゃ活用</li>
<li>一緒に遊ぶ</li>
</ul>

<h3>4. 15分ルール</h3>
<ul>
<li>視聴</li>
<li>遊び</li>
<li>運動</li>
</ul>

